# PlanetScale Database Skills (workspace)

This project includes the PlanetScale Database Skills in `.cursor/skills/database-skills/`. Use them when working with databases in this workspace.

## When to use which skill

- **MySQL / InnoDB** — Schema, indexes, queries, migrations, replication, locking, connections → read `.cursor/skills/database-skills/mysql/SKILL.md` and apply its guidance.
- **PostgreSQL** — Schema design, indexing, MVCC/VACUUM, WAL, replication, monitoring, connection pooling → read `.cursor/skills/database-skills/postgres/SKILL.md`.
- **Vitess** — Sharding, VSchema, keyspaces, online DDL, VReplication, MySQL scaling → read `.cursor/skills/database-skills/vitess/SKILL.md`.
- **Neki** (sharded Postgres) — Scaling/sharding Postgres → read `.cursor/skills/database-skills/neki/SKILL.md`.

## Invoking from chat

You can also invoke the plugin skills with `/mysql`, `/postgres`, `/vitess`, or `/neki` (plugin must be enabled in settings).
